# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:4
translate spanish work0_f28cee14:

    # "Immediately after finishing up my classes for the day, I head out to the car and drive over to the Law Offices, where my new job is."
    "Inmediatamente después de terminar mis clases del día, salgo al coche y conduzco hasta el bufete de abogados, donde está mi nuevo trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:7
translate spanish work0_5a8d723c:

    # "I walk in to work. Dana is sitting in the lobby. I wave hello to her."
    "Entro al trabajo. Dana está sentada en la recepción. La saludo con la mano."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:8
translate spanish work0_468fc973:

    # cw "Hey there new guy. [pcname], wasn't it?"
    cw "Hola, chico nuevo. [pcname], ¿no?"

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:9
translate spanish work0_749220c3:

    # pc "That's me."
    pc "Ese soy yo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:10
translate spanish work0_9e8ad45b:

    # cw "Mrs. Mills is back in her office. Go right ahead. Hope you have a good day."
    cw "La Sra. Mills está en su despacho. Pasa. Espero que tengas un buen día."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:11
translate spanish work0_efe7c8fa:

    # pc "Thanks, you too."
    pc "Gracias, tú también."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:13
translate spanish work0_58488fe0:

    # "I go back to Mrs. Mills' office."
    "Vuelvo al despacho de la Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:15
translate spanish work0_532a1db6:

    # "She sits at her desk, barely glancing up at me when I walk in."
    "Está sentada en su escritorio y apenas me mira cuando entro."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:17
translate spanish work0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_goodafternoon.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_goodafternoon.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:18
translate spanish work0_640a0bfd:

    # bs "Good afternoon. I hope you're ready to work."
    bs "Buenas tardes. Espero que estés listo para trabajar."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:19
translate spanish work0_c24d08f6:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am, I am."
    pc "Sí, señora, lo estoy."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:20
translate spanish work0_cc9bf2b9:

    # bs "Good."
    bs "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:22
translate spanish work0_4d725376:

    # "I spend most of the day cleaning. The place had gotten pretty bad over the few weeks where she didn't have an assistant and Mrs. Mills wants the place to be spotless."
    "Me paso casi todo el día limpiando. El lugar se había descuidado bastante durante las semanas en las que no tuvo asistente y la Sra. Mills quiere que todo esté impecable."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:23
translate spanish work0_e7ab64bb:

    # "I dust everything, wipe every surface, vacuum the floor, and organize all the paperwork."
    "Limpio el polvo de todo, froto cada superficie, paso la aspiradora por el suelo y ordeno todo el papeleo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:25
translate spanish work0_67f863e2:

    # "Afterwards, Mrs. Mills has me type all her notes while she dictates. Luckily, I'm a fast typist because she is a fast talker and doesn't slow down at all."
    "Después, la Sra. Mills me hace escribir a máquina todas sus notas mientras me dicta. Por suerte, escribo rápido porque ella habla rápido y no baja el ritmo en absoluto."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:26
translate spanish work0_cec5844a:

    # "Finally, when it is time to go, she looks over the notes that I had typed and gives a little nod."
    "Por fin, cuando llega la hora de irme, revisa las notas que he mecanografiado y asiente ligeramente con la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:30
translate spanish work0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:31
translate spanish work0_7e667a4e:

    # bs "You did good work today. Keep it up and maybe you'll be able to stick around here for a while."
    bs "Hoy has hecho un buen trabajo. Sigue así y quizá puedas quedarte aquí un tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:32
translate spanish work0_a9a2d1b9:

    # pc "Thanks."
    pc "Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:33
translate spanish work0_cd3b9566:

    # bs "See you tomorrow."
    bs "Hasta mañana."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:34
translate spanish work0_a5da4cbe:

    # pc "Okay, goodbye, Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Vale, adiós, señora Mills."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:37
translate spanish work0_bab3cfa9:

    # "I walk out and down the hall to the lobby. There, Dana is still working, sorting paperwork at her desk."
    "Salgo y recorro el pasillo hasta el vestíbulo. Allí, Dana sigue trabajando, clasificando papeleo en su escritorio."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:38
translate spanish work0_7c1acf53:

    # pc "Goodnight Dana."
    pc "Buenas noches, Dana."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:40
translate spanish work0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:41
translate spanish work0_68df17d0:

    # cw "Oh, goodnight, [pcname]. See you tomorrow."
    cw "Oh, buenas noches, [pcname]. Nos vemos mañana."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:43
translate spanish work0_ef83833d:

    # "I go outside and stand in front of the building for a moment, breathing the fresh air."
    "Salgo y me quedo un momento delante del edificio, respirando el aire fresco."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:44
translate spanish work0_9dec6a30:

    # "It has been a long day and I'm exhausted. And this is only the first. Every weekday is going to be like this basically, leaving me only the evenings to do whatever I want."
    "Ha sido un día largo y estoy agotado. Y esto es solo el principio. Básicamente, todos los días laborables van a ser así, dejándome solo las tardes para hacer lo que quiera."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:45
translate spanish work0_d7ac5816:

    # "So, what do I want to do now?"
    "Entonces, ¿qué quiero hacer ahora?"

